msgid "# triton.language.get_element"
msgstr "# triton.language.get_element"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：根据给定的索引，从输入张量中读取单个元素。\n"
"原型：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Reads a single element from the input tensor based on the given index.\n"
"Prototype:\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.get_element(\n"
"    src,\n"
"    indice,\n"
"    _builder=None,\n"
"    _generator=None\n"
") -> scalar\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:8
msgid "可以作为tensor的成员函数调用，如`x.get_element(...)`，与`get_element(x, ...)`等效。"
msgstr "It can be called as a member function of a tensor, such as `x.get_element(...)`, which is equivalent to `get_element(x, ...)`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `src`        | `tensor`          | 要被访问的源张量                                                     |\n"
"| `indice`       | `tuple of ints` 或 `tuple of tensors`    | 用于指定元素位置的索引                                                    |\n"
"| `_builder` |- | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                            |\n"
"| `_generator`   | -               | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                                |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Description |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `src`        | `tensor`          | The source tensor to be accessed                                |\n"
"| `indice`       | `tuple of ints` or `tuple of tensors` | Indices used to specify element positions                       |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now         |\n"
"| `_generator`   | -               | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now         |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`scalar`：与 `src` 张量元素类型相同的标量值\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`scalar`: A scalar value of the same element type as the `src` tensor.\n"

