#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:24
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:26
msgid ""
"支持任意形状的张量，但需满足：\n"
"`indice` 的长度必须与 `src` 张量的维度数相同。\n"
msgstr ""
"Supports tensors of arbitrary shape, with the following requirement:  \n"
"The length of `indice` must be equal to the number of dimensions of the `src` tensor.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:28
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/get_element.md:30
